featured_reviews.review_id: The best Masjid in the surrounding areas following Quran n Hadeeth. Jumma bayan in Tamil, rarely in Urdu. Jumma timing @ 12:45pm, Separate arrangement for sisters in the first floor. Shaoor available for odd days and on Shawal 6 days,Arafat,  Aasura, and Ifthar available for Ramadan, Shawal, Arafat, Aasura. Tharavi prayers 8 Rakath and then bayan for one hour. Odd days extra Urdu bayan and whole night you can do any ibadath. Eclipse prayers conducted. Madarasa and free tuition also available. Rooms available for bachelors. For sisters islamic studies course is available which the batch starts after Ramadan every year.
